{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSPredicate","text":"NSPredicate","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"predicate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the style layer’s predicate to include only the features in the source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer that satisfy a condition that you define. If the style layer initially"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"comes from the style, its predicate corresponds to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"filter"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in the style JSON."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See the “"},{"type":"text","text":"Predicates and Expressions"},{"type":"text","text":"”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"guide for details about the predicate syntax supported by this class."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","level":3,"text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To filter the layer to include only the features whose ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"index"},{"text":" attribute is 5","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or 10 and whose ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ele"},{"text":" attribute is at least 1,500, you could create an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSCompoundPredicate"},{"text":" along these lines:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let layer = MLNLineStyleLayer(identifier: \"contour\", source: terrain)","layer.sourceLayerId